s="fas fa-external-link-square-alt ms-1"></i></a>。</p>]]></description></item><item><title>站点参数</title><link>https://hbs.razonyang.com/v1/zh-hans/docs/configuration/site-params/</link><pubDate>Sat, 27 Nov 2021 19:53:24 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://hbs.razonyang.com/v1/zh-hans/docs/configuration/site-params/</guid><description>&lt;p>站点参数文件默认为 &lt;code>config/_default/params.toml&lt;/code>。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>站点配置</title><link>https://hbs.razonyang.com/v1/zh-hans/docs/configuration/site/</link><pubDate>Sat, 27 Nov 2021 19:53:24 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://hbs.razonyang.com/v1/zh-hans/docs/configuration/site/</guid><description>&lt;p>站点配置文件默认为 &lt;code>config/_default/config.toml&lt;/code>。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>图像处理</title><link>https://hbs.razonyang.com/v1/zh-hans/docs/image-processing/</link><pubDate>Sun, 15 Aug 2021 14:19:06 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://hbs.razonyang.com/v1/zh-hans/docs/image-processing/</guid><description>&lt;p>本文提供一些调整图片大小、裁剪和对齐图片的用例。&lt;/p></description><enclosure url="https://hbs.razonyang.com/v1/en/docs/image-processing/featured-sample.webp" length="498412" type="image/webp"/></item><item><title>Alert Shortcode</title><link>https://hbs.razonyang.com/v1/zh-hans/docs/shortcodes/alert/</link><pubDate>Thu, 22 Oct 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hbs.razonyang.com/v1/zh-hans/docs/shortcodes/alert/</guid><description>&lt;p>本文将介绍如何使用 &lt;code>alert&lt;/code> shortcode。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>